  Trace dump:
  = ./../tests/test-framework.sh:7270:error()
  = sanity-quota.sh:156:quota_error()
  = sanity-quota.sh:5917:test_75()
  = ./../tests/test-framework.sh:7643:run_one()
  = ./../tests/test-framework.sh:7706:run_one_logged()
  = ./../tests/test-framework.sh:7524:run_test()
  = sanity-quota.sh:5927:main()
Dumping lctl log to /tmp/ltest-logs/sanity-quota.test_75.*.1747779128.log
Dumping logs only on local client.
