Warning: it is not recommended to have a squash value outside of the offset range [ 0, -3 ] as it will not be mapped properly.
On MGS 192.168.121.219, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;default&lt;/span&gt;.admin_nodemap = nodemap.&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;default&lt;/span&gt;.admin_nodemap=0
waiting 10 secs &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; sync
FAIL 75 (69s)


== sanity-quota test 76: project ID 4294967295 should be not allowed ========================================================== 22:12:19 (1747779139)
Waiting &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; MDT destroys to complete
Creating test directory
lfs mkdir: dirstripe error on &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;/mnt/lustre/d76.sanity-quota&apos;&lt;/span&gt;: Operation not permitted
lfs setdirstripe: cannot create dir &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;/mnt/lustre/d76.sanity-quota&apos;&lt;/span&gt;: Operation not permitted
 sanity-quota test_76: @@@@@@ FAIL: setup quota failed with 1 
